{"ts":"2026-06-27T07:18:11.787Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Designing Dashboard Interface**\n\nI am now designing the interface for the \"Cryptographic Ledger & Invoice Operations\" center, focusing on the needs of GFF AI System Admins like Dr. Sarah Vance. I'm centering the dashboard around a \"Hardware-Attested Ledger\" visual metaphor. The visual language features charcoal panels, dark background grains, neon blue/teal active streams, and crisp white typography. I will integrate an SVG pipeline illustrating the secure invoice process. I'm strategizing the layout to include a custom administrative hero banner and an interactive visual blueprint.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
