{"ts":"2026-06-27T07:18:17.728Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Implementing Mobile-First Design**\n\nI'm now implementing the mobile design strategy. The \"Create Invoice Drawer\" is integrated with Framer Motion for smooth right-to-left slide-in transitions. I've added a glowing progress indicator during invoice creation, providing feedback while signing with the HSM key. On mobile, the table will scroll horizontally with indicators, or render simplified card structures, and filters are responsive. Sliders and drawers will use full-screen overlays on touch devices. I'm focusing on modifying `app/admin/billing/page.tsx` while being careful not to touch the existing mock data file.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
